    <h1>Project Overview</h1>
    <p>
        Our current project serves as a robust foundation for building applications using <strong>.NET Core 8</strong>. Designed with versatility and scalability in mind, it offers a comprehensive suite of features that streamline the development process and enhance functionality.
    </p>

    <h2>Key Features:</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Authentication &amp; User Management:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Secure Authentication:</strong> Implements industry-standard authentication mechanisms to ensure user security.</li>
                <li><strong>User Management:</strong> Facilitates efficient handling of user accounts, roles, and permissions, allowing for seamless administration.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Complete CRUD Operations:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Create, Read, Update, Delete:</strong> Provides full-fledged CRUD functionalities, enabling developers to manage data effortlessly across various entities.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>URL Encryption:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Secure URL Handling:</strong> Encrypts URLs to protect sensitive information and maintain data integrity during client-server interactions.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Advanced Grids with Excel Export:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Data Grids:</strong> Features interactive and responsive data grids that enhance data presentation and user interaction.</li>
                <li><strong>Excel File Downloads:</strong> Allows users to export grid data directly to Excel, facilitating easy data analysis and reporting.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>PDF Generation:</strong>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Automated PDF Creation:</strong> Enables the generation of PDF documents from application data, supporting reporting, invoicing, and documentation needs.</li>
            </ul>
        </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Choose This Project?</h2>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Built on .NET Core 8:</strong> Leverages the latest advancements in .NET Core 8, ensuring high performance, cross-platform compatibility, and future-proof architecture.</li>
        <li><strong>Open and Free to Use:</strong> This project is <strong>completely free</strong> and <strong>open-source</strong>, making it accessible to developers worldwide. Whether you're building a small application or a large-scale enterprise system, our project provides the essential building blocks you need.</li>
        <li><strong>Easy to Customize:</strong> Designed with flexibility in mind, you can easily tailor and extend the functionalities to meet your specific project requirements.</li>
        <li><strong>Community Driven:</strong> Join a growing community of developers who contribute to and support the project, fostering an environment of collaboration and continuous improvement.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>
            <strong>Clone the Repository:</strong>
            <pre><code>git clone https://github.com/TmArkaji/BaseWebApplication.git</code></pre>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Install Dependencies:</strong>
            <p>Navigate to the project directory and install the necessary dependencies.</p>
            <pre><code>cd BaseWebApplication
dotnet restore</code></pre>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Run the Application:</strong>
            <pre><code>dotnet run</code></pre>
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Explore and Customize:</strong>
            <p>Begin building your application by leveraging the provided features and customizing them to fit your needs.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>

